<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gitloh ziekin ka Lalpa'n A thuok hi,
 Thawkna gen sen ei puoi;
 Liemna gen sen ei puoi:
 Aw, A mel deihum thisan a suok zo tai.

[V2]
 Van Lal chan a thuok ie (2)
 Zepna chun a zep ui;
 Kilhna thikzum leh naka liem thuokin,
 Lalpa thanmuol a liempih tau.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa thihna hi kawlkim ah gen viel un,
 Sim leh mal mite'n le;
 A thawkna thu za leu,
 &quot;Aw Lalpa&quot; tiin kah la hun lem un au.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa liem thavaih aw hung gihawih tak chu,
 Nuoi simlei a thawnga;
 Thisa thelbang thawhsak,
 Aw khulsina sietlei ana changsa haw.

[V5]
 4. Dahum gensen loh thuokin ei hung tan tai,
 Henkawl nang bang ei sut;
 Man in ei hung chaw tai,
 Aw, I pau gam lam ah ei puilut kit tai.

[V6]
 5. Ka hinna tuolthing leh ka nawpna Na hi,
 Na vanglim thing ka bel,
 Na bakah chawl ingka,
 Aw, Salem thak ah nuom takin leng tangka.</lyrics>
<title>Van Lal Cha'n A Thuok ie</title>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>70</hymn_number>
</song>